## Diff Review Checklist — Run Before Accepting Any Change

```
□ Did it modify files I didn't mention?
□ New dependencies added that aren't in package.json?
□ Used getSession() instead of getUser() in server code?
□ Used request.json() in a Stripe webhook? (must be request.text())
□ Used browser Supabase client (lib/supabase/client.ts) in a Server Component?
□ Changed a function signature that other files depend on?
□ Added middleware.ts inside /app instead of project root?
□ Does the logic match my INTENT, not just my literal words?
□ Anything "technically correct but wrong for this codebase"?
```

If any box is checked → reject, refine the prompt, run again.

